  <name>COSMIC Connect</name>
  <summary>Connect and sync your devices with COSMIC Desktop</summary>

  <description>
    <p>
      COSMIC Connect provides seamless integration between your Android devices and COSMIC Desktop,
      enabling device synchronization, file sharing, notification mirroring, clipboard sync, and more.
    </p>
    <p>Features include:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Device Discovery - Automatic detection of devices on your network</li>
      <li>Secure Pairing - TLS certificate exchange with user verification</li>
      <li>File Sharing - Send and receive files between devices</li>
      <li>Clipboard Sync - Synchronize clipboard content across devices</li>
      <li>Notification Mirroring - See phone notifications on your desktop</li>
      <li>Battery Monitoring - Track battery status and charge state</li>
      <li>Media Control - Remote control media playback (MPRIS)</li>
      <li>SMS Messaging - Compose and send text messages from desktop</li>
      <li>Camera as Webcam - Use your phone camera as a virtual webcam</li>
      <li>Remote Input - Control your device remotely</li>
      <li>Remote Desktop - VNC-based screen sharing between desktops</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      This package includes the COSMIC Connect Manager for device management, a panel applet for
      quick access, and a background daemon for handling device communication.
    </p>
    <p>
      Note: The daemon component may have limited functionality within the Flatpak sandbox.
      For full functionality, consider installing the native package for your distribution.
    </p>
  </description>

